        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 block md:hidden">
          <div class="neon-bleed-border rounded-2xl p-6 relative overflow-hidden group">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-primary)]/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-[#A3E635] uppercase tracking-wider">CRO · Her zaman</span>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[hsl(210,10%,90%)] mb-3 mt-1">Dönüşüm Optimizasyonu</h3>
            <div class="text-sm text-[hsl(215,16%,58%)] leading-relaxed space-y-1">
              <p>Web sitenizden gelen başvuruları artırın.</p>
